reviewText:
A good suspense movie. No blood and guts just pure intense suspense taking place on a plane.
No monsters either - just an intense movie that will keep you on the edge of your seat.
If you like all the blood and gore they show today then this will be to mild for you.

Forget I Know What You Did Last Summer, this is the one thriller to see. Ciccillian Murphy is an awesome bad guy. He reminded me a little bit of Jack Nicholson in one scene and Rachel McAdams is very dramatic and intense as well in this one. Also, Jayma Mays is in here as well-didn't recognize her at first with much longer hair. Great thrill ride or should I say flight, the whole way.
By far my favorite Cillian Murphy movie!
A very unique film, with an excellent twist. You will enjoy this movie
I liked this movie. But, for me, it's not one that I would enjoy watching over and over again. Product was delivered quickly and in superb condition.
Thought is was a very good movie

Well thought out, and taut, Red Eye really delivers. Its "clean"; Nothing you have to be embarrassed by, if viewing with younger kids.
Wes Craven is way more than just a horror director! All the acting is top-notch.
This movie is one of my favorites.  Cillian Murphy is one scary bad guy.  Rachel McAdams is very good, too.  A lot of suspenseful moments.
Really good/intense movie, had me on the edge.
I love Cillian & Rachel in this movie.

I'm female and 78 years old.  I was very pleased with the movie, and Amazon service.  I could not get the movie from Redbox, nor from my local library.  I watched the movie by my self and I screamed at the point where the girl, while in the airplane stabed the guy.  It came as a suprise.  I liked the way the girl handled herself in  a dangerous situation.  She was spiritually and physically strong.  For me it was a good movie.
Not your typical Wes Craven movie. Found it interesting, but not any edge of my seat moments. An OK movie for an OK price. Not a bad movie, just not a great movie. B.Beckner
Brilliant thriller from Wes Craven (RIP)
awesome thriller.  both Cillian Murphy and Rachel McAdams gave excellent performances.
Thank you

loved the delivery time, excellent package, and we enjoyed the movie. well order other movies. Thank you
What can I say, I have a thing for bad guys. Cillian Murphy is about as sexy as a bad guy can get in this movie. A+++++++++
